data.description: This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence offers a perfect blend of modern elegance and comfortable living. Step into an inviting open-concept design, where the spacious living area seamlessly flows into the dining space and kitchen, creating an ideal environment for both entertaining and everyday living. The heart of this home is the beautifully appointed kitchen featuring granite countertops, providing a luxurious touch to the space.  You'll appreciate the stylish stained concrete floors that not only add a touch of sophistication but also ensure easy maintenance and durability. The well-thought-out split floorplan allows for privacy, with the primary bedroom situated on one side of the home and the secondary bedrooms on the other. Escape to the primary suite, a spacious retreat boasting a private en-suite bathroom, offering a haven of relaxation with its spa-like ambiance. The additional two bedrooms share a thoughtfully designed second bathroom, perfect for accommodating family or guests. This home also features a convenient 2-car garage, providing secure parking and additional storage space, fenced back yard, and covered back patio. Located in a quiet cul-de-sac.
